data.description: SELLER OFFERING $5000 TOWARD BUYERS CLOSING COST!  WELCOME HOME!  You will fall in love with this Move In Ready Home Located in the Community of Grayson Park, minutes from Five Forks, Downtown Simpsonville, Shopping, Restaurants, Schools and Medical Offices.  This home sits on a .30 acre premium private lot and will not disappoint with all the charm you could ask for.  This amazing 5 bedroom, 3 full bath offers an amazing floor plan with countless upgrades and you will begin to fall in love as soon as you pull in the driveway.  Upon entering the home you will be greeted with amazing curb appeal and mature landscaping which gives this home a sleek look. Entering the home you will be greeted with an amazing foyer with elegant trim, hardwood floors, and neutral paint throughout.  The kitchen has all the upgrades with granite countertops, beautiful high end cabinets, backsplash tile, stainless appliances, large pantry, gas stove and plenty of counter space to accommodate all your cooking and entertainment needs.  Open to the kitchen you will fall in love with the living room space that offers a fireplace with gas logs for all your cozy nights.  On the main level this home also offers a dining room, an office | formal sitting area, x large mud room, plus a bedroom and full bath that is perfect for a Mother N Law Suite if that was a need.  The Second level offers 4 more bedrooms, 2 full baths, laundry and a loft ~ flex room.  If you are looking for a Master Retreat we have it for you!  The oversized master bedroom is spacious with plenty of square footage to slip off for a little quiet time and relaxation.  The master also delivers a extra large walk in closet, a double granite vanity, garden tub, and separate shower.   And if you need a cozy spot for your morning coffee we have you covered!  Located off the back of the house you will find a large covered patio gazebo area to enjoy some nature and beautiful views.  This home also offers a fully fenced in back yard and a 3 car garage for extra parking or storage needs.  Don't miss out on this beautiful jewel!  Let's make this your FOREVER HOME!  Call today for your private showing.
